  "lyrics": "It's about your community, yeah About something It's about you and me And the freedom we hold inside It's about us all If you believe It's true, it's true Baby, I see you somewhere I know inside You're all I need Oh, and you're wishing well Oh, it's what it's like Because you're all spent up And your soul is gone But you can't reach the light Oh, now, inside, now, please The dark things inside your mind They tell you that you're just not right The dark things inside your mind They tell you not to spit on the soul Fight that shit with all you got I got another come up and what you want It's the easy way out All the mysteries and lies Worth seeing all about, hey I don't wanna come up, don't wanna play up Don't wanna tell you not what's on my mind You wanna be the face of I ain't lying, I ain't lying, I ain't dying And I'm just dying, crying inside And I don't fucking know why I don't know why with all the love And all the things inside for a minute To choose to throw it away for a disaster Inside for a thousand grand And for another hundred grand To get you killed for a twenty-four moment Get you up, yeah And take your bitch too That's what I'm talking about I bust with the words Like, look at these things that we're saying to each other Look at how we fight every day And go for everything that we think is right What you say ain't fucked up, mom Fuck the fame You can have it back, motherfucker Just know it's not my name Don't wanna be that fake front Don't wanna be the thing that says That you can't trust me So would you hold me Imagine if I helped you see And I don't know what would Make it better for me Oh, baby, you know that touch's good Oh, baby, you know that love is good Tell me, little man You know that love is good Don't wanna be the person That hurts the woman next to me Wanna be a better man For my son inside of my life You see, got a new perspective Maybe it's that I was the one that I think By looking at my life from A way through another Take one side of the glass in my arm Waiting for me Still in the dark With a drug and a shot in my heart Yeah, I'm still in the motherfucking dark I don't wanna fuck it up for you or me I don't wanna fuck it up for anyone But I guess I already did it You hear that? I guess I already did it Yeah If you find a better way to keep me in your heart A new design, I'm sorry For all my things that I don't know What the fuck? The line I take The line I see It's a line like I'm out evenly Ain't no contradiction here It's just me",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 5.260000228881836,
      "text": "It's about your community, yeah",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 7.300000190734863,
      "text": "About something",
      "start": 5.260000228881836
    },
    {
      "end": 12.279999732971191,
      "text": "It's about you and me",
      "start": 8.739999771118164
    },
    {
      "end": 16.219999313354492,
      "text": "And the freedom we hold inside",
      "start": 13
    },
    {
      "end": 20.540000915527344,
      "text": "It's about us all",
      "start": 16.639999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 24.280000686645508,
      "text": "If you believe",
      "start": 21.65999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 29.280000686645508,
      "text": "It's true, it's true",
      "start": 25.280000686645508
    },
    {
      "end": 38.720001220703125,
      "text": "Baby, I see you somewhere",
      "start": 34.15999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 42.84000015258789,
      "text": "I know inside",
      "start": 40.279998779296875
    },
    {
      "end": 46.47999954223633,
      "text": "You're all I need",
      "start": 43.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 51.279998779296875,
      "text": "Oh, and you're wishing well",
      "start": 48.279998779296875
    },
    {
      "end": 54.939998626708984,
      "text": "Oh, it's what it's like",
      "start": 51.279998779296875
    },
    {
      "end": 60.540000915527344,
      "text": "Because you're all spent up",
      "start": 57.040000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 63.560001373291016,
      "text": "And your soul is gone",
      "start": 60.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 70.27999877929688,
      "text": "But you can't reach the light",
      "start": 64.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 73.73999786376953,
      "text": "Oh, now, inside, now, please",
      "start": 70.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 75.37999725341797,
      "text": "The dark things inside your mind",
      "start": 73.73999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 77.5,
      "text": "They tell you that you're just not right",
      "start": 75.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 79.5,
      "text": "The dark things inside your mind",
      "start": 77.5199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 81.94000244140625,
      "text": "They tell you not to spit on the soul",
      "start": 79.5
    },
    {
      "end": 83.73999786376953,
      "text": "Fight that shit with all you got",
      "start": 81.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 87.22000122070312,
      "text": "I got another come up and what you want",
      "start": 83.73999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 90.55999755859375,
      "text": "It's the easy way out",
      "start": 88.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 93.86000061035156,
      "text": "All the mysteries and lies",
      "start": 91.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 96.5,
      "text": "Worth seeing all about, hey",
      "start": 93.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 100.62000274658203,
      "text": "I don't wanna come up, don't wanna play up",
      "start": 98.23999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 103.72000122070312,
      "text": "Don't wanna tell you not what's on my mind",
      "start": 100.62000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 105.9800033569336,
      "text": "You wanna be the face of",
      "start": 103.73999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 108.18000030517578,
      "text": "I ain't lying, I ain't lying, I ain't dying",
      "start": 105.9800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 110.81999969482422,
      "text": "And I'm just dying, crying inside",
      "start": 108.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 114.5,
      "text": "And I don't fucking know why",
      "start": 112.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 116.5,
      "text": "I don't know why with all the love",
      "start": 114.69999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 118.26000213623047,
      "text": "And all the things inside for a minute",
      "start": 116.5
    },
    {
      "end": 120.69999694824219,
      "text": "To choose to throw it away for a disaster",
      "start": 118.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 122.31999969482422,
      "text": "Inside for a thousand grand",
      "start": 120.69999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 124.0999984741211,
      "text": "And for another hundred grand",
      "start": 122.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 126.08000183105469,
      "text": "To get you killed for a twenty-four moment",
      "start": 124.0999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 129.10000610351562,
      "text": "Get you up, yeah",
      "start": 126.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 131.0800018310547,
      "text": "And take your bitch too",
      "start": 129.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 132.22000122070312,
      "text": "That's what I'm talking about",
      "start": 131.0800018310547
    },
    {
      "end": 133.22000122070312,
      "text": "I bust with the words",
      "start": 132.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 135.25999450683594,
      "text": "Like, look at these things that we're saying to each other",
      "start": 133.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 136.82000732421875,
      "text": "Look at how we fight every day",
      "start": 135.25999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 138.83999633789062,
      "text": "And go for everything that we think is right",
      "start": 136.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 140.66000366210938,
      "text": "What you say ain't fucked up, mom",
      "start": 138.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 142.6199951171875,
      "text": "Fuck the fame",
      "start": 141.39999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 144.89999389648438,
      "text": "You can have it back, motherfucker",
      "start": 143.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 146.8000030517578,
      "text": "Just know it's not my name",
      "start": 144.89999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 149.36000061035156,
      "text": "Don't wanna be that fake front",
      "start": 147.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 151.16000366210938,
      "text": "Don't wanna be the thing that says",
      "start": 149.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 152.82000732421875,
      "text": "That you can't trust me",
      "start": 151.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 157.55999755859375,
      "text": "So would you hold me",
      "start": 155
    },
    {
      "end": 159.74000549316406,
      "text": "Imagine if I helped you see",
      "start": 157.6999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 162.1999969482422,
      "text": "And I don't know what would",
      "start": 159.74000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 164.25999450683594,
      "text": "Make it better for me",
      "start": 162.47999572753906
    },
    {
      "end": 168.25999450683594,
      "text": "Oh, baby, you know that touch's good",
      "start": 164.25999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 172.25999450683594,
      "text": "Oh, baby, you know that love is good",
      "start": 168.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 175.1199951171875,
      "text": "Tell me, little man",
      "start": 173.5399932861328
    },
    {
      "end": 178.13999938964844,
      "text": "You know that love is good",
      "start": 175.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 182.13999938964844,
      "text": "Don't wanna be the person",
      "start": 180.4199981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 183.89999389648438,
      "text": "That hurts the woman next to me",
      "start": 182.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 185.82000732421875,
      "text": "Wanna be a better man",
      "start": 184.39999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 187.9600067138672,
      "text": "For my son inside of my life",
      "start": 185.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 190.0800018310547,
      "text": "You see, got a new perspective",
